Build, Test and Deploy to Github Container Registry

This workflow will test, build and deploy a new version of the dual-job-date container to Github Container Registry.
Jobs
build

This job will build the application and cache the nuget packages
Actions used in build job

    uses: actions/checkout@v2
    uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v1
    uses: actions/cache@v2

test

This job will test the application.
Actions used in test job

    uses: actions/checkout@v2
    uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v1

build-and-push-docker

This job will build the application and upload image to the registy.
Actions used in build job

    uses: actions/checkout@v2
    uses: docker/login-action@v3
    uses: actions/cache@v4
    uses: docker/build-push-action@v5

Cache
This workflow uses a cache to store the nuget packeges.